🛠 Architecture Overview
Your system includes:
✅ Camera Feed – Captures live video
✅ Flask Server – Processes video frames
✅ YOLO Model – Detects objects (e.g., people, intruders)
✅ Email Notification – Sends alerts when a person is detected
✅ GUI Interface – Displays real-time detection

📌 System Flow
1️⃣ Camera captures video → Frames sent to Flask
2️⃣ Flask processes frames → YOLO detects objects
3️⃣ If person detected → Trigger Email Notification
4️⃣ Display result in GUI
